.NET Framework 4.6.name: SDLanguageItemCollection
.NET Framework 4.6.summary: Represents a collection of language specific elements.

methods.name: GetElementOrDefault(string language)
methods.summary: Gets the element of the given language, if it exists. Otherwise the default language element or null.
methods.returns: The element of the given language, if it exists. Otherwise the default language element, if it exists. Otherwise null.
